{"title":"谚语","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":2,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"谚语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小时偷针，大时偷金。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邻家失火，不救自危。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若要断酒法，醒眼看醉人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要打当面鼓，莫敲背后锣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人直有人逢，路直有人走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三日不读书，语言也无味。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打人二日忧，骂人三日羞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舍不得金弹子，打不了凤凰鸟。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}